    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'Eater of Worlds: Reach a hunger multiplier of 4x.


    No Lunch Break:
    Spend every waking hour of the day with an overfilled stomach.


    Miss Piggy:
    Digest 8000 calories in one day.


    Mucho Texto: Have a total of 18L or more
    in your stomach and intestines.


    Take That, Triple Finish: Get filled with
    the maximum amount of baby batter.


    Opening Kickoff: Experience your first
    fetal movement.


    The Morning After: Wake up with your stomach still overfilled
    from last night.


    Elastigirl: Reach the highest possible stretching multiplier.


    That''s
    No Moon: Reach the largest possible belly size.


    Queen of Kebabs: Earn a
    total of $10000 from streaming.


    Seed of Destiny: Deliver a perfectly healthy
    baby.


    Full Term: Reach the end of the last day of pregnancy.'
